# Silent Briefing Design System

Full spec: `@design/README.md`. These are the non-negotiable rules.

## Tokens (always use CSS variables — never hardcode values)

```css
/* Colors */
--primary: #000f22           /* deep navy */
--primary-container: #0a2540
--secondary: #b6191a         /* crimson — signal only, <5% viewport */
--tertiary: #d4af37          /* gold — pinstripes, accents, focus rings */
--surface: #fbf9f5           /* cream paper */

/* Type scale (use token names) */
--display-2xl, --display-lg, --headline-lg, --headline-md
--title-lg, --body-lg, --body, --body-sm
--label-md   /* 12px / UPPERCASE / 0.2em tracking / 700 weight */
--label-sm   /* 10px / UPPERCASE / 0.3em tracking / 700 weight */

/* Spacing: --space-1 (4px) through --space-32 (128px) */
/* Radii: --radius-sm (2px), --radius-md (4px), --radius-lg (8px), --radius-xl (12px) */
/* Shadows: --shadow-sm, --shadow-md, --shadow-lg, --shadow-glow-gold */
```

Import: `import '@/../../design/colors_and_type.css'` (or configure path alias).

## Typography Rules

- **Headlines:** Newsreader, sentence case, italic for emphasis, NEVER all-caps.
- **Labels:** Inter, UPPERCASE, `letter-spacing: 0.2–0.3em`, font-weight 700, 10–12px.
- **Body:** Inter, sentence case, 15–17px.
- **Numbers:** always `font-variant-numeric: tabular-nums`.
- Do NOT create a third font family.

## The No-Line Rule

**Do not use `1px solid` borders to separate content areas.** Instead:
- Use tonal background shifts: `--surface-container-low` on `--surface`.
- Ghost border only when required: `1px solid rgba(0, 15, 34, 0.08)`.
- Gold pinstripe: `1px solid var(--tertiary)` — vertical accents only (left-hand ruler, featured card left-edge on hover).
- Focus ring: `2px solid var(--tertiary)`, 4px offset — always visible on keyboard.

## Cards

```css
background: var(--surface-container-lowest);
border-radius: var(--radius-lg);  /* 8px */
border: none;                      /* No-Line Rule */
box-shadow: var(--shadow-sm);
/* Hover: */
box-shadow: var(--shadow-md);
/* Featured: 2px top border only */
border-top: 2px solid var(--tertiary);
/* Hover left-accent (animated) */
border-left: 2px solid var(--tertiary);
```

## Portraits

```css
img.portrait { filter: grayscale(1); transition: filter 600ms ease; }
img.portrait:hover { filter: grayscale(0); }
```

## Icons

- Lucide only. Stroke: 1.5px. Sizes: 16px (inline), 20px (buttons), 24px (nav), 32px (empty states).
- Never Material Symbols.

## Interactions

- Hover: left gold pinstripe appears (200ms), no scale, no color flip.
- Button hover: `brightness(1.08)`.
- Focus: 2px gold outline, 4px offset.
- Disabled: 40% opacity, `cursor: not-allowed`.
- Animation: 3 families only — screen enter (opacity+y, 400ms), list hover (left-pinstripe, 200ms), stagger (60ms/child, 300ms each). One stagger per screen.

## Copy Rules (enforce in UI strings)

- No emoji. No 🚨 🔴 ⚠️ — use Lucide `alert-circle` / `alert-triangle`.
- Sentence case for headlines. UPPERCASE for metadata labels only.
- No hype: never "supercharged", "seamless", "powered by AI", "unlock", "effortless".
- Empty state: italic serif. `"No filings on record for this cycle."`
- Loading: name the source. `"Extracting from utcourts.gov…"`
- Error: show when. `"Source unreachable — last successful fetch: 14:02 MT"`

## Glassmorphism (only on sticky chrome)

```css
background: rgba(251, 249, 245, 0.80);
backdrop-filter: blur(16px) saturate(1.2);
/* no border, no shadow — blur alone creates lift */
```
